result.title: the love of Vietnamese people
result.content: Now is 4:05 am in Viet Nam, and I with my friend is waiting the rating changed by the contest Round #359. My family have been sleep for a long time but I still wait. Tomorrow, I must go to school but by the love of codeforces, I am still awake. If you can, you can push the time of contest early so the Vietnamese coders can do more contest. Thanks you very much !!!
